{"tid":891674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太古樓價大插20%　銀行銀主盤插價14%","createTime":"2018-11-06T10:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:35:42.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f4bd0f0b069ff8614276a47c6ba51de7fef281a","tid":891674,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181106/20539403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539403&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f182dbb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539403&h=9ebf571e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181106/20539403</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20181106/720pix/1541440507_e085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20181106%2F720pix%2F1541440507_e085.jpg&h=058096bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/DUpQKv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FDUpQKv&h=62529301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/RU4wpD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FRU4wpD&h=50eaa606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/EesZM3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEesZM3&h=884163ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】二手樓價由「日日升」變「日日跌」，而且減價潮由細價樓蔓延至中價樓，就連向來以樓價硬淨見稱的鰂魚涌太古城亦大跌價。11月首宗成交即驚見三房單位賣「兩房價」，劈價兩成；同區南豐新邨有三房戶劈足百萬仍無人承接。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181106/large/06bm01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F06bm01p.jpg&h=39a16191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓市滿佈陰霾，太古城不少業主減價離場。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181106/20539406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539406&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2e294228\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539406&h=a961a72c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181106/20539406</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】樓市吹淡風，連龍頭滙豐銀行也減價沽售銀主盤。尖沙嘴港景峯一個銀主盤，經過多次拍賣後，最終銀主也要劈價求售，創屋苑今年新低價。<br />\n<br />\n九龍站豪宅成交死寂，上月僅擎天半島一宗「自讓盤」成交，市況淡靜下，銀主盤也要劈價求售。銀主為滙豐銀行，低於市價仍無人問津。本報於滙豐銀行網站為該銀主盤估價，今次滙豐沽貨比自己估值還要低出14%。"},{"pid":"2d436b28119aea042a36fcc42d61ade7a4c7036c","tid":891674,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"太古咁舊唔計"},{"pid":"165b5fe0f0c5e940c269709277f13ccc047dbccc","tid":891674,"uid":45148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d436b28119aea042a36fcc42d61ade7a4c7036c","tid":891674,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"太古咁舊唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"十大屋苑都可以唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e224885b58b47452eb37f4c220d8ba57e53289","tid":891674,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d436b28119aea042a36fcc42d61ade7a4c7036c","tid":891674,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"太古咁舊唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"其實香港冇樓住得人"},{"pid":"b2352f24a817283adde1b4d0b6dc96d3d5b3ec97","tid":891674,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"咁少"},{"pid":"9e4c66db002cb1ca4bd5f39cd3e75774dc1cff44","tid":891674,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"唔計呀"},{"pid":"5c8300226a4c864e1060400800e864d973c3475d","tid":891674,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:28:12.000Z","msg":"太古999年唔計"},{"pid":"27ff3209b5e4cd7013c0f54419583a4fd43f33f7","tid":891674,"uid":51719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"四十年樓，美金二千一呎，七百呎柏文，美金一百四十萬，足夠收息美金五千一個月，左右全部工薪階層。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}